data.description: Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this spacious virtually new, two-story home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths is great for anyone seeking convenience and comfort. Step inside to discover an updated interior with an open concept layout, excellent for entertaining guests or simply relaxing. Outdoors, you'll find a fire pit, ample outdoor space for gardening, BBQs and pets. Plus, with its proximity to the casino and a golf course, this home offers the perfect blend of entertainment and relaxation. Don't miss out on this beautiful home!
